    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make June 22nd (or the day after Nightclubs reopen) a bank holiday",
        "additional_details": "This would minimise the disruption the next day. We've missed many bank holidays so this additional one would not only be a huge boost to morale, but also, to the economy.",
        "background": "In light of the proposed roadmap, nightclubs in England are set to reopen on Monday the 21st of June. I propose the day after be declared a bank holiday. This will give nightclubs the boost they deserve after over a year of closure.",
